quran[25{c,v,t}:
78,31,be shak parhaiz gaaron ke liye kamyabi hai
78,32,( yani ) baagh aur angoor
78,33,aur hum Umar nojawan aurtain
78,34,aur sharaab ke chalakte hue glass
78,35,wahan nah behooda baat sunen ge nah jhoot ( khurafaat )
78,36,yeh tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se sila hai inaam kaseer
78,37,woh jo asmano aur zameen aur jo un dono mein hai sab ka maalik hai bara meharban kisi ko is se baat karne ka yaara nahi hoga
78,38,jis din rooh ( al-ameen ) aur farishtay saf bandh kar kharray hon ge to koi bol nah sakay ga magar jis ko ( khuday-e rehman ) ijazat bakhshay aur is ne baat bhi durust kahi ho
78,39,yeh din barhaq hai. pas jo shakhs chahay apne perwar-digaar ke paas thikana bana ye
78,40,hum ne tum ko azaab se jo anqareeb anay wala hai aagah kar diya hai jis din har shakhs un ( aamaal ) ko jo is ne agay beje hon ge dekh le ga aur kafir kahe ga ke ae kash mein matti hota
79,1,un ( firshton ) ki qasam jo doob kar khech letay hain
79,2,aur un ki jo aasani se khol dete hain
79,3,aur un ki jo tertey phirtay hain
79,4,phir lapak kar agay barhatay hain
79,5,phir ( duniya ke ) kamon ka intizam karte hain
79,6,( ke woh din aa kar rahay ga ) jis din zameen ko bhonchal aeye ga
79,7,phir is ke peechay aur ( bhonchal ) aeye ga
79,8,is din ( logon ) ke dil khaif ho rahay hon ge
79,9,aur ankhen jhuki hui
79,10,( kafir ) kehte hainkiya hum ultay paon phir lout jayen ge
79,11,bhala jab hum khokhli haddiyan ho jayen ge ( to phir zindah kiye jayen ge )
79,12,kehte hain ke yeh lootna to ( mojab ) zayan hai
79,13,woh to sirf aik daant hogi
79,14,is waqt woh ( sab ) maidan ( hashar ) mein aa jama hon ge
79,15,bhala tum ko moose ki hekiyaat pohanchi hai
